## Outputs

Depending on the selected workflow stage, the orchestrator generates:

- Intermediate CSV files
- Quality-control reports
- Standardized datasets
- GIS-linked outputs
- Neighborhood-level aggregated statistics

Intermediate outputs are preserved to support auditing, validation, and human-in-the-loop review.
